        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR1h0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T09:33:43.313+09:00">子貢說， 「我不願意別人對我無理;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:06:58.603+09:00">我也不願意對別人無理。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:09:00.435+09:00">你還沒有做到這個地步呀!</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:07:55.565+09:00">孔子說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_005-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-25T07:08:01.171+09:00">「賜呀，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-11T20:52:08.885+09:00">孔子說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:47:09.294+09:00">「由， 我教你的、你都能知道麼?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:47:15.85+09:00"> 你知道的、你就以為『知道』;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:47:20.064+09:00">你不知道的、你就以為『不知道』.•</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-03-09T05:47:27.425+09:00"> 這就是真正的「知道』!」子</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:00.368+09:00">子貢問國家政治的事情。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:25.04+09:00">孔子說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:30.293+09:00">「輝食充足;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:35.165+09:00">軍備充實;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:42.573+09:00">人民信任政府。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:35:51.03+09:00">子責說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:36:03.754+09:00">「在不得已要減省的時候，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:36:07.465+09:00">這三件事情里邊那一件可以先去?」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:36:14.688+09:00">孔子說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:36:20.73+09:00">「去了軍備。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:36:52.317+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:38:44.009+09:00">子貢又說:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:37:02.096+09:00">「在不得已要減省的時候，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:37:12.476+09:00">這二件事情里邊那一件可以先去?」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:38:51.895+09:00">孔子說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:38:58.74+09:00">「去了糧食。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-14a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:40:03.658+09:00">從古以來，人生都有一死.只要人民信任政府，即使糧食偶然不足，人民或還可以為國家效命;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_012-15a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-08-30T04:40:27.538+09:00">但若人民對政府沒有信心，則人民對商家必不能有貞圓的志操!」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:18:36.991+09:00">叶公向子路问孔子的做人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-24a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:19:33.147+09:00">他好像不知道老年就快来临似的。"【「云爾」二字實難解;在這章意似略同現代語「好像•••••• 似的」。2011: 云尔"二字没有确解，在这章意似略同现代语"好像……似的"。】</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:18:41.919+09:00">子路没有回答他。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:18:46.371+09:00">孔子对子路说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:18:51.085+09:00">"你为什么不对他这样说呢！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:19:00.12+09:00">他的做人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:19:24.668+09:00">用起功来连饭也忘记吃，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:19:31.682+09:00">时常高兴得使一切忧愁都消失了，</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
